channel.description: ok i have a error.. my items arent showing up xD its like they are invisible... i can still put them on and everything but i cannot see them in my bank/bag/invitory screen so if you think you can fix this go for it O.o if not ill just start over on a different source

item.title: W00t i gotz me a strange error
item.dc:creator: @I_Metal_I I Metal I
item.description:
@I_Metal_I wrote:

heathtech:

It could be a packet loss of some sort. Check your cases and make sure they are not overriding any other cases (Usually Java catches this). Also sometime calling to much from the instream can cause information loss too the client (That might go for the outstream as well). If you were following a tut and this happened, either delete everything you just put on from the tut, or cut your losses and do whatever you have to do to get back to normal. Sorry dude.

lol its fine itll take a hour to remake all of the source… since ive done it once xD
